{"tid":2056295,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局指中小學第二階段復課大致運作正常","createTime":"2020-06-08T14:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T14:44:55.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae1a3f7cf2a3dbf67b803142cf2b076f3a57b9e","tid":2056295,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"教育局指中小學第二階段復課大致運作正常<br />\n2020-06-08 HKT 21:41<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，已聯絡中學及小學了解第二階段復課的情況，大致上運作正常。<br />\n<br />\n至於早前一度出現確診個案的瀝源邨祿泉樓，附近學校今日有部分學生缺席；教育局說，理解家長的關注，學校已加強防疫措施，並彈性處理學生告假申請。教育局一直與衞生防護中心及附近學校跟進情況，醫學專家意見亦認為復課安排，可如期嚴謹地進行。<br />\n<br />\n教育局說，會繼續與沙田區有關學校及衞生防護中心，保持緊密聯絡，呼籲學校繼續實施各項衞生防護措施。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530906-20200608.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530906-20200608.htm&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19tfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=02092a74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530906-20200608.htm&h=c05f6575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530906-20200608.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">學業要緊，支持復課，應該盡快回復全日上學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fe656762c8cf86ab3f4ea4931e89ce3cf9182ec3","tid":2056295,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"第三波攬炒正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3164344ca13f74cac408734513707f5a2882a2da","tid":2056295,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe656762c8cf86ab3f4ea4931e89ce3cf9182ec3","tid":2056295,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"第三波攬炒正式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2